author: butek
msg: We eventually want to only generate those files that are referenced.
SymTabEntry.isReferenced() is meant for this task.  Up to now, though,
The changes here are the first step to generating only those files that are referenced:
going through the symbol table to determine what's referenced by what.
1.  Make the writers query this flag before generating files.
2.  Make sure things are generated even if the WSDL isn't complete (ie., doesn't have
all of service, binding, portType, message, types).
3.  Make sure setting noImports works with this new feature.
